axes.label: Combat Efficiency Index
axes.description: Measures offensive efficiency — how much impact per engagement.

narrative.headline: You convert fights when allies collapse.
narrative.body: Kill participation and KDA outpace your role cohort, but isolated duels still punish overextensions.

telemetry.focus: Allied engages convert at 68% claim rate; solo duels convert at 41%.

axes.emptyCopy: No combat metrics available for this window.

axes.label: Objective Reliability Index
axes.description: How consistent you are in helping secure major objectives.

narrative.headline: Objective setups are clean when vision is prepped.
narrative.body: Dragon and Baron participation stay above cohort averages, but smite steals against you still slip through without ward denial.

telemetry.focus: Control wards placed before objectives: 3.4 per setup.

axes.emptyCopy: No objective events recorded in the selected matches.

axes.label: Survival Discipline Index
axes.description: Ability to minimize unnecessary deaths and adapt defensively.

narrative.headline: Positional slips snowball when tempo breaks.
narrative.body: Death share rises sharply after mid-game picks, signaling regroup timings should tighten once outer turrets fall.

telemetry.focus: Deaths spike when regroup timers exceed 30 seconds after a pick.

axes.label: Vision & Awareness Index
axes.description: Tracks how you control vision and deny enemy information.

narrative.headline: Vision control drives objective reliability.
narrative.body: You keep wards placed and killed above cohort averages; opportunity is expanding sweep timings around second herald.

telemetry.focus: Vision denial before Baron occurs in 62% of setups.

axes.label: Economy Utilization Index
axes.description: Measures how efficiently you convert gold into map pressure.

narrative.headline: Gold rarely sits idle.
narrative.body: You convert item spikes into damage faster than the cohort. Late backs during losing streaks still delay third core spikes.

telemetry.focus: Third item timing averages 23:40 when ahead, 26:05 when behind.

narrative.headline: Middle and midline stabilize, other roles remain volatile.
narrative.body: Secondary roles have lower win rate and KDA variance spikes; stay disciplined when swapping off comfort picks.

telemetry.focus: KDA variance spikes to 0.41 on top-adapt attempts.

axes.label: Momentum Index
axes.description: Captures streak patterns — momentum and recovery.

narrative.headline: Momentum surges, but recovery climbs are slower.
narrative.body: Two-win streaks convert into five-game claims, yet back-to-back losses extend to four without an intervention.

telemetry.focus: Momentum drops sharply after two losses—reset routines needed to shorten slumps.

axes.emptyCopy: No streak data for this sample.

axes.label: Composure Index
axes.description: Evaluates consistency between best & worst matches.

narrative.headline: Performance swings remain large.
narrative.body: Top quartile games carry hard; bottom quartile drop-offs are equally deep—focus on stabilizing baseline impact.

telemetry.focus: Loss-side deaths surge to 6; tighten mid-fight exit calls to reduce variance.

axes.emptyCopy: Variance metrics unavailable for this window.

insights: Economy Utilization Index is your strongest foundation—gold rarely sits idle.
Composure Index needs attention—performance swings remain large.
Solid core with room for growth—focus on shoring up weak points.
